327
00:19:49,724 --> 00:19:50,813
Automobiles.

328
00:19:51,544 --> 00:19:52,674
How are you?

329
00:19:53,237 --> 00:19:55,440
Um, I work as a decorator.

330
00:19:55,906 --> 00:19:56,907
How exciting.

331
00:19:57,169 --> 00:19:59,144
