360
00:22:52,717 --> 00:22:53,957
Hello, lovely.

361
00:23:01,512 --> 00:23:02,876
Happy Valentine's.

362
00:23:04,450 --> 00:23:07,149
- That's so sweet.
- I got your little note.

363
00:23:07,269 --> 00:23:08,800
Well, Hildy did.

364
00:23:10,820 --> 00:23:13,565
Be careful about
just putting things in my bag.

365
